sentence: On August 11, 2014, astronomers released studies, using the Atacama Large Millimeter / Submillimeter Array (ALMA) for the first time, that detailed the distribution of Hydrogen cyanide, Hydrogen isocyanide, Formaldehyde, and dust inside the comae of comet s C / 2012 F6 (Lemmon) and C / 2012 S1 (ISON).
